      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/sri-lanka-to-start-restructuring-talks-with-investors-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，全球投资者和斯里兰卡官员预计下周将开始谈判，旨在重组价值 120 亿美元的全球违约债券。该国的美元债券上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/sri-lanka-to-start-restructuring-talks-with-investors-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 20:03:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
